        "translation": "\"A Buddha is one who takes awakening and knowledge as his meaning.",
        "source": "X88n1646_011:0203a12_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "因心而成。",
        "translation": "It's produced from the mind.",
        "source": "X88n1646_011:0203a12_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不可以諸相見也。",
        "translation": "It can't be viewed in terms of characteristics.",
        "source": "X88n1646_011:0203a13_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經云。",
        "translation": "The sūtras say.",
